p.k: Unikitty hosts a live music video countdown show for the kingdom, presenting the ecstatic audience with the top 4 music videos in the Unikingdom, featuring our favorite characters. / The gang puts their favorite items in a Time Capsule to send 100 years in the future, but they get stuck inside right before the door seals. / A mysterious relative, Uncle Donklecorn, shows up unexpectedly, claiming to be family. / After Unikitty finds out that tourism is down in the Unikingdom, she recruits the gang to make a tourism video to inspire people to visit the kingdom. / The moon is bored of taking the nightshift, since everyone's always asleep. So Unikitty leads the gang in putting on an over-the-top late night talk show to keep the moon occupied.
